WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
ARGENTINA.
1. S/V MIRABAUD DISMASTED AND WITHOUT NAVIGATION LIGHTS
   IN 39-43S 056-55W AT 181830Z MAR. VESSELS IN
   VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST
   IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO ANY COASTAL RADIO STATION.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 426/11(24) AND 445/11.
